
================================================================================

movieinfo - get some basic movie file info

DESCRIPTION
    I was having trouble getting basic movie info such as dimensions of
    screen. This is a collection of hacks to do so.

USAGE
    movieinfo [OPTIONS]..

            -h                      help

  USAGE EXAMPLES
       movieinfo ./movie.avi

